{
  "title": "Tabela de Velocidade de Corte",
  "htmlContent": "<div class=\"complex-table-wrapper\">\n    <h4>Velocidade de Corte (Vc) em m/min, em função do avanço (s)</h4>\n    <table class=\"complex-table\">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th rowspan=\"2\">Material</th>\n          <th colspan=\"5\">Velocidade de corte (m/min.)</th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Ferramenta</th>\n          <th>0,1</th>\n          <th>0,2</th>\n          <th>0,4</th>\n          <th>0,8</th>\n          <th>1,6</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr class=\"group-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">METAIS FERROSOS</td></tr>\n        <tr class=\"subgroup-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">AÇO CARBONO</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">até 500N/mm²</td><td>HSS</td><td>-</td><td>60</td><td>45</td><td>34</td><td>25</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>280</td><td>236</td><td>200</td><td>170</td><td>67</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">até 700N/mm²</td><td>HSS</td><td>-</td><td>44</td><td>32</td><td>24</td><td>18</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>240</td><td>205</td><td>175</td><td>145</td><td>50</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">até 900N/mm²</td><td>HSS</td><td>-</td><td>32</td><td>24</td><td>18</td><td>13</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>200</td><td>170</td><td>132</td><td>106</td><td>34</td></tr>\n        <tr class=\"subgroup-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">AÇO LIGA E FUNDIDO</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">até 900N/mm²</td><td>HSS</td><td>-</td><td>34</td><td>25</td><td>19</td><td>14</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>150</td><td>118</td><td>95</td><td>75</td><td>23</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">até 1250N/mm²</td><td>HSS</td><td>-</td><td>24</td><td>17</td><td>12</td><td>8,5</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>118</td><td>108</td><td>85</td><td>71</td><td>24</td></tr>\n        <tr class=\"group-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">METAIS NÃO FERROSOS</td></tr>\n        <tr class=\"subgroup-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">ALUMÍNIO</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">Alumínio puro</td><td>HSS</td><td>400</td><td>300</td><td>200</td><td>118</td><td>75</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>1320</td><td>1120</td><td>950</td><td>850</td><td>710</td></tr>\n        <tr class=\"subgroup-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">BRONZE</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">210 a 260N/mm²</td><td>HSS</td><td>-</td><td>63</td><td>53</td><td>43</td><td>34</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>355</td><td>280</td><td>236</td><td>200</td><td>180</td></tr>\n        <tr class=\"subgroup-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">LATÃO</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">Latão comum</td><td>HSS</td><td>350</td><td>300</td><td>250</td><td>200</td><td>150</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>900</td><td>800</td><td>700</td><td>600</td><td>500</td></tr>\n        <tr class=\"subgroup-header\"><td colspan=\"7\">COBRE</td></tr>\n        <tr><td rowspan=\"2\">Cobre puro</td><td>HSS</td><td>250</td><td>200</td><td>150</td><td>100</td><td>80</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>MD</td><td>700</td><td>600</td><td>500</td><td>400</td><td>300</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <br>\n    <h4>Tabela de Velocidade de Corte (V) para o Torno</h4>\n    <table class=\"complex-table simple-param-table\">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th rowspan=\"2\">MATERIAIS</th>\n          <th colspan=\"3\">FERRAMENTAS DE AÇO RÁPIDO</th>\n          <th colspan=\"2\">FERRAMENTAS DE CARBONETO-METÁLICO</th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th>DESBASTE</th>\n          <th>ACABAMENTO</th>\n          <th>ROSCAR/RECART.</th>\n          <th>DESBASTE</th>\n          <th>ACABAMENTO</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td>AÇO 1020</td><td>25</td><td>30</td><td>10</td><td>200</td><td>300</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>AÇO 1045</td><td>20</td><td>25</td><td>8</td><td>120</td><td>160</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>FERRO FUNDIDO MALEÁVEL</td><td>20</td><td>25</td><td>8</td><td>70</td><td>85</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>FERRO FUNDIDO DURO</td><td>10</td><td>15</td><td>6</td><td>30</td><td>50</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>BRONZE</td><td>30</td><td>40</td><td>10-25</td><td>300</td><td>380</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>LATÃO E COBRE</td><td>40</td><td>50</td><td>10-25</td><td>350</td><td>400</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>ALUMÍNIO</td><td>60</td><td>90</td><td>15-35</td><td>500</td><td>700</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <br>\n    <h4>Observações</h4>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Consulte sempre o fabricante da ferramenta para valores específicos.</li>\n      <li>Valores podem variar conforme refrigeração, tipo de máquina e acabamento desejado.</li>\n      <li>Para materiais especiais, como titânio e inox, reduza a velocidade em 30%.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>"
}
